title: Multi-vehicle accident closes M20
text:
The M20 coastbound has been closed at Junction 8 near Maidstone because of a crash between a car and a van. London-bound traffic could also be delayed to allow an air ambulance to land.
Cars are being diverted onto the A20. Traffic for Dover could exit at Junction 7 and use the A249 and M2 instead.
It's the second time the stretch of motorway has been closed in the past 24 hours.
Last updated Thu 15 Oct 2015 Travel Kent
